{"tid":528842,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS/AN] 修羅道-Shurado- (1) 日本硬派刀劍手遊","createTime":"2018-01-14T09:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T08:43:19.000Z","uid":11844,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d45ce12e7d9b6b423878a71e56be71dd7ccac654","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T09:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/57/0001606157.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F57%2F0001606157.JPG&h=8e80f87f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遊戲簡介(轉自巴哈): [url]<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/9/157169.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2F9%2F157169.html&d=VJDn%2BW9awTT4qQJ7EVJ3II9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=3aeb4623\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/9/157169.html</a> <br />\n[/url] <br />\nGANBARION 在 12 月 25 日正式推出同公司第二款智慧型手機平台作品《修羅道（Shurado）》（iOS / Android），本作是一款讓玩家挑戰一對一的戰鬥，目標是從地獄之底爬上巔峰的武器動作戰鬥遊戲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n畫面:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/60/0001606160.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F60%2F0001606160.JPG&h=585f0b22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/00/a56ffd8cd92b46b3f635a2fc0c7zie84.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F00%2Fa56ffd8cd92b46b3f635a2fc0c7zie84.JPG&h=25c55562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/06/92527dcc96767636fdae9a39f4dziee4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F06%2F92527dcc96767636fdae9a39f4dziee4.JPG&h=e7475c6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/07/4a79876ed9b5a7aae07ac508eb4zief4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F07%2F4a79876ed9b5a7aae07ac508eb4zief4.JPG&h=2a7956d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下載地址<br />\nIOS: [url<a href=\"https://goo.gl/noGw42[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FnoGw42%5B%2Furl%5D&d=VJDn%2BW9awTT4qQJ7EVJ3II9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=b6f370e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/noGw42[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\nAN:<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/SDF43b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FSDF43b&d=VJDn%2BW9awTT4qQJ7EVJ3II9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=fad6d907\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/SDF43b</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近年難得一見嘅佳作, 技術型手游<br />\n原本以為玩法同infinity blade相似, 點知完全唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n操作十分簡單 但易學難精<br />\n敵人難度可以話係手機入面嘅dark soul<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可惜題材比較冷門 同埋無點賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出咗成半個月都未有人講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻game絕對值得一玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24cbda20f4b06f4b1d1f79b04fd01526f61fc202","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T09:47:31.000Z","msg":"IOS:<a href=\"https://goo.gl/noGw42\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FnoGw42&d=VJDn%2BW9awTT4qQJ7EVJ3II9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=c00e5b53\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/noGw42</a>"},{"pid":"075c9805a649760b14338707e8e2630519c87d83","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:14:01.000Z","msg":"玩咗兩日 暫時玩到23關<br />\n<br />\n過咗第10關會開羅生門, 呢個模式難好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下講下心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先呢隻game最重要係兩條bar <br />\n上面藍色係HP<br />\n下面綠色係STA (stamina 氣)<br />\n打人同格擋都會扣氣 所以要好小心用<br />\n<br />\n畫面左下角會有個壺, 係比你裝額外嘅藍色魂(HP)<br />\n戰鬥時可以用佢回血<br />\n<br />\n行路同跑步可以點人物隻腳黎切換<br />\n途中會遇到好多鬼火, 藍色=回hp, 黃色=錢<br />\n<br />\n有時打之前留意下敵人身後嘅樓梯<br />\n如果有白色火=好多錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n武器暫時有三種: <br />\n<br />\n太刀 - 快 低攻 耗氣少 格擋弱 <br />\n鉈 - 快 耗氣中等 格擋中等 追擊快 (追擊:格擋完嘅第一下攻擊速度)<br />\n斧頭 - 慢 耗氣高 高攻 高防<br />\n<br />\n高階武器會有屬性<br />\n<br />\n分別係 火，水，雷，光，暗<br />\n<br />\n火克水<br />\n水克雷<br />\n雷克火<br />\n<br />\n光暗互克<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每把相同武器嘅能力值可以相差 5+- 左右 (唔肯定)<br />\n<br />\n途中打完敵人佢地會跌箱 <br />\n最低級嘅=20mins<br />\n中級=6hrs<br />\n銀箱=12hrs<br />\n金箱=24hrs (應該係普通模式最高)<br />\n羅生門箱=48hrs (要過咗羅生門先拎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n每開夠20個箱就會開多一個位擺箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打住咁多先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0be07932ccac76c9ebcacd9f1816e6b20add60d","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334dd4f7ad001123cc99abfd95b5438974db0673","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:29:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe34641b5cf91e719f8f53b51c93c9616785282","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5ea82e1d622b245eb23c1b54224ff5873c5171","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:41:26.000Z","msg":"唔洗課金架 好玩過infinity blade啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6c9d6bf9439ee7e5704ec473c98ec7b7e99bf9","tid":528842,"uid":103717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:01:28.000Z","msg":"單機game?"},{"pid":"65ae5824c749364262f8c928e3755305a071c084","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee6c9d6bf9439ee7e5704ec473c98ec7b7e99bf9","tid":528842,"uid":103717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:01:28.000Z","msg":"單機game?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:48:30.000Z","msg":"係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4b34af09573d5c7ad87fca0ea53680de464ea6","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ab044fbc080d857c79e3f3dc62c143db7c7ea1","tid":528842,"uid":66506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:44:05.000Z","msg":"試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db28cf853c3f513d20caf3e677643c179db9caa","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5ab044fbc080d857c79e3f3dc62c143db7c7ea1","tid":528842,"uid":66506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:44:05.000Z","msg":"試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T14:10:34.000Z","msg":"多謝捧場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31f654835cf5bb03e23d321bb7b809e5b089024","tid":528842,"uid":18123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T15:12:20.000Z","msg":"試下先"},{"pid":"189cd3af0cbfd0b451fe7a8b5d9d3b56e59e12da","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T15:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9bb9527246afb173a233b71c980623954d9db9c","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T15:52:24.000Z","msg":"啱啱過咗羅生門<br />\n<br />\n總共有6關<br />\n<br />\n死咗/過關之後要6個鐘頭先可以再入羅生門<br />\n<br />\n第三關會同自己嘅複製人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過咗羅生門後會跌一個要開48hrs 嘅箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d91b81867c4ad3b3d08d47285d41dfc0ff058b","tid":528842,"uid":66506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T23:52:18.000Z","msg":"樓豬，想問點樣可以格檔反擊？sta bar 突出嘅綠色部分代表啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879e5bd8c0085a45a9946abba2f0f52e483bb94f","tid":528842,"uid":18123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T06:49:36.000Z","msg":"有冇人都係用iphone6玩？<br />\n佢話我部機唔support..."},{"pid":"58563c3b53dc04959ee7b63a6c00f9b27816e27d","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"42d91b81867c4ad3b3d08d47285d41dfc0ff058b","tid":528842,"uid":66506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T23:52:18.000Z","msg":"樓豬，想問點樣可以格檔反擊？sta bar 突出嘅綠色部分代表啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"要睇準佢落刀個下黎禁<br />\n佢個判定好嚴格 應該係敵人起手完0.3秒左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n判定成功會出紫色特效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be1d4f201887949d71d11317d2c8704fd1724cb","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"879e5bd8c0085a45a9946abba2f0f52e483bb94f","tid":528842,"uid":18123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T06:49:36.000Z","msg":"有冇人都係用iphone6玩？<br />\n佢話我部機唔support..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T06:55:33.000Z","msg":"我用iphone6s 佢個相容性個度錯撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係ip6s - iphonex 先support<br />\n所以你睇佢評價個度全部屌佢iphone6 玩唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n遊戲本身好玩 但評價比呢樣野拉低就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37917bfe1b0976a5a1cd558eeb58992c0862238","tid":528842,"uid":21305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:00:04.000Z","msg":"V20 都玩唔撚到? ON9?"},{"pid":"7d5be4c3b6be8780e5cb45bee4c8fcba217771ee","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58563c3b53dc04959ee7b63a6c00f9b27816e27d","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"42d91b81867c4ad3b3d08d47285d41dfc0ff058b","tid":528842,"uid":66506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T23:52:18.000Z","msg":"樓豬，想問點樣可以格檔反擊？sta bar 突出嘅綠色部分代表啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"要睇準佢落刀個下黎禁<br />\n佢個判定好嚴格 應該係敵人起手完0.3秒左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n判定成功會出紫色特效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:00:21.000Z","msg":"Stamina bar 總值係綠色嘅<br />\n而同佢重疊個part 淺色啲嘅就係=回stamina嘅速度<br />\n<br />\n當你打人 stamina跌得低過重疊個part, 淺色bar會跟住佢跌 <br />\n淺色bar短咗 = 回氣回慢咗<br />\n<br />\n所以點樣分配stamina呢個方面 同一味鳩劈嘅infinity blade玩法分別好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89971f60fa70a8327b6ac90b12540b661c2d06db","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b37917bfe1b0976a5a1cd558eeb58992c0862238","tid":528842,"uid":21305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:00:04.000Z","msg":"V20 都玩唔撚到? ON9?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"咁食硬件? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁睇黎相容性呢方面係敗筆了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d3aeebef6cff740cc8f4d004fb85cbb998c18b","tid":528842,"uid":21305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89971f60fa70a8327b6ac90b12540b661c2d06db","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b37917bfe1b0976a5a1cd558eeb58992c0862238","tid":528842,"uid":21305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:00:04.000Z","msg":"V20 都玩唔撚到? ON9?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"咁食硬件? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁睇黎相容性呢方面係敗筆了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:02:33.000Z","msg":"我已經AN7.0 V20 都DOWN唔到<br />\n<br />\n睇黎大把人玩唔到"},{"pid":"fd5643be883b4714caf7ca1d4f0fc22c2603b204","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31d3aeebef6cff740cc8f4d004fb85cbb998c18b","tid":528842,"uid":21305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89971f60fa70a8327b6ac90b12540b661c2d06db","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b37917bfe1b0976a5a1cd558eeb58992c0862238","tid":528842,"uid"