:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T23:52:18.000Z","msg":"樓豬，想問點樣可以格檔反擊？sta bar 突出嘅綠色部分代表啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"要睇準佢落刀個下黎禁<br />\n佢個判定好嚴格 應該係敵人起手完0.3秒左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n判定成功會出紫色特效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:00:21.000Z","msg":"Stamina bar 總值係綠色嘅<br />\n而同佢重疊個part 淺色啲嘅就係=回stamina嘅速度<br />\n<br />\n當你打人 stamina跌得低過重疊個part, 淺色bar會跟住佢跌 <br />\n淺色bar短咗 = 回氣回慢咗<br />\n<br />\n所以點樣分配stamina呢個方面 同一味鳩劈嘅infinity blade玩法分別好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:51:12.000Z","msg":"補充:<br />\n<br />\n有回stamina技能嘅武器<br />\n<br />\n條淺色bar會短啲 = 用氣唔會咁快用埋回氣bar<br />\n<br />\n同埋回氣嘅時候 因為淺色bar短啲 所以會回得快啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頭盔: 個人理解 有錯歡迎指正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"124b21cde297e3270ef0892bcb47a34893785896","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:59:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n更新: <br />\n<br />\n下面綠色係STA (stamina 氣)<br />\n打人<del>同格擋都</del>會扣氣 所以要好小心用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">格擋唔會扣氣<br />\n而係扣耐久度</span> (禁實自己出o個個紅圈)<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a9d2651a84843b61bf89bab5eb1ed18bb869995c","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T08:51:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66dda2510fadcfd4b67a7815612374bc99615ba4","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e14e6e10551b97a0da5f80434fe7d3d7523e2d","tid":528842,"uid":66506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:54:54.000Z","msg":"死Q左會冇晒黃玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪我一路打上去一路用啲玉來升武，就可以永久食左落支武度架？<br />\n<br />\n另外打打下想quit game (return to title)會唔會冇晒進度？"},{"pid":"2f5b595d93fa4a8e659a78711dc2fcd88bc7cd8e","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92e14e6e10551b97a0da5f80434fe7d3d7523e2d","tid":528842,"uid":66506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:54:54.000Z","msg":"死Q左會冇晒黃玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪我一路打上去一路用啲玉來升武，就可以永久食左落支武度架？<br />\n<br />\n另外打打下想quit game (return to title)會唔會冇晒進度？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T10:08:41.000Z","msg":"係 所以話佢似dark soul<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n升級把武器最多可以去到+5 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係賣嘅錢都係一樣 (有商人 分叉路口隨機遇到)<br />\n<br />\n唔會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n打完quit game佢會自動save 進度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17c3907479de80b818c23ddbd2f954132b8423b","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T10:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf494f102a0ecdbe49a200b324b4411f14b84a53","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T11:07:37.000Z","msg":"打完敵人之後<br />\n<br />\n會出現分叉路口<br />\n<br />\n大家會留意到分叉路口會有兩隻獅子雕像<br />\n<br />\n唔同獅子雕像代表敵人強度 同埋敵人跌落嘅武器,經驗值高低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.nakamap.com/img/groupchat.assets/221fe4142c387c99033e9c9899cc17f8df6183a8_raw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.nakamap.com%2Fimg%2Fgroupchat.assets%2F221fe4142c387c99033e9c9899cc17f8df6183a8_raw.jpg&h=f76c2a69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強度如下: <br />\n<br />\n青苔石 -&gt; 石頭 -&gt; 紅色 -&gt; 銀色 -&gt; 紅金色(Boss) -&gt; 黑金色 (跳關Boss)<br />\n<br />\n當中黑金色嘅係跳關boss, 打贏佢會跳10關 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而商人會隨機出現, 分叉路口會有個告示牌話你知呢條路有商人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/18/47224ce31a6407bc360b9cdc035zieq4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F18%2F47224ce31a6407bc360b9cdc035zieq4.JPG&h=2cd74af4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n賣嘅野有 <br />\n<br />\n強化素材 (細&amp;大晶石)<br />\n武器<br />\n同埋傳送石 (比你落翻低層)<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/19/f49f3516cff636007930d05617czier4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F19%2Ff49f3516cff636007930d05617czier4.JPG&h=c1d2b1a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56b8b44eda2971945517222ac2392997d8a53565","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T12:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b186326d14bba6b5ecb890f0567b8a715130c8e","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf18b395680ee41e7996dd9d489d4045ae649e5","tid":528842,"uid":66506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:34:48.000Z","msg":"幫你推下喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLV 1 斧勁過LV 2 鉈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21322dd7d240712d302636951ee20958aa91981b","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbf18b395680ee41e7996dd9d489d4045ae649e5","tid":528842,"uid":66506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:34:48.000Z","msg":"幫你推下喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLV 1 斧勁過LV 2 鉈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T16:02:39.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前期黎講斧頭高攻係優點黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後期毒鉈磨死boss好有用 我都練緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c98f38c4a856050c99779dc78429d2473dde013","tid":528842,"uid":84369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T22:44:22.000Z","msg":"係咪練鉈最好？<br />\n我一直都係玩緊太刀<br />\n玩到廿幾打得耐擋唔到一兩野就死撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n番去低層果舊石其實幾時用最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 隻game堅好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ae5f0b910b92b42483383724784c0802672c1b","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"486bcea46810caf3f99630bc51c743e1bf98a93e","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d5be4c3b6be8780e5cb45bee4c8fcba217771ee","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58563c3b53dc04959ee7b63a6c00f9b27816e27d","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"要睇準佢落刀個下黎禁<br />\n佢個判定好嚴格 應該係敵人起手完0.3秒左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n判定成功會出紫色特效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:00:21.000Z","msg":"Stamina bar 總值係綠色嘅<br />\n而同佢重疊個part 淺色啲嘅就係=回stamina嘅速度<br />\n<br />\n當你打人 stamina跌得低過重疊個part, 淺色bar會跟住佢跌 <br />\n淺色bar短咗 = 回氣回慢咗<br />\n<br />\n所以點樣分配stamina呢個方面 同一味鳩劈嘅infinity blade玩法分別好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:51:12.000Z","msg":"補充:<br />\n<br />\n有回stamina技能嘅武器<br />\n<br />\n條淺色bar會短啲 = 用氣唔會咁快用埋回氣bar<br />\n<br />\n同埋回氣嘅時候 因為淺色bar短啲 所以會回得快啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頭盔: 個人理解 有錯歡迎指正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T00:34:43.000Z","msg":"更正:<br />\n<br />\n我搞錯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淺色bar係代表開技所需要嘅stamina (開技=左右同時禁)"},{"pid":"e9cf97f9315371c1a5a9fcacfeb22016d2e9d462","tid":528842,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c98f38c4a856050c99779dc78429d2473dde013","tid":528842,"uid":84369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T22:44:22.000Z","msg":"係咪練鉈最好？<br />\n我一直都係玩緊太刀<br />\n玩到廿幾打得耐擋唔到一兩野就死撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n番去低層果舊石其實幾時用最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 隻game堅好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T00:37:41.000Z","msg":"鉈檔嘅速度好似係最快<br />\n但唔似斧頭咁會有半秒延遲<br />\n技術需求高咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人認為斧頭前期有優勢<br