)上次闖關失敗嘅黃魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而商人就多數係第6層 / 1字尾層數出現<br />\n<br />\n暫時黎講我都係6 11 21層見過商人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:09:52.000Z","msg":"商人好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無屬性果啲武器我會賣出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來爆左箱位無得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我果個仲要係羅生門個48hr箱"},{"pid":"e51e73103cb97574a6d4348252fd8d723a658f69","tid":528842,"uid":66506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/222639_d0d1dcbbb46f6f0d825d4c2966bf03d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F222639_d0d1dcbbb46f6f0d825d4c2966bf03d0.jpg&h=fa32f71d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/222643_56d947d4959fccd1fe4637430fac058b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F222643_56d947d4959fccd1fe4637430fac058b.jpg&h=7de0dac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊把鉈好D? LV2 個把鉈其實係咪辣殺來?<br />\nhighlight 左藍色既效果又代表D 咩??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}